_:N63a81575a1644a56b584816350bce84d <http://schema.org/description> "United Kingdom Security Vetting (UKSV) is the single government provider of National Security Vetting (NSV). We are the centre of excellence for security vetting and enable government to protect citizens and provide vital public services, by understanding and managing personnel security risks." .
